Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.weaponry.targets

Class Target

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.model.weaponry.targets.Target
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TargetCell, TargetPlayer, TargetRoom
    public abstract class Target
extends java.lang.Object
    Targets are the actors that have a role in attacks. Each AttackModule has a list of Targets, each of which corresponds to a choice made by the attacker. Targets can be Rooms, Cells or Players.
